  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and soak them in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Heat the clay pot over medium heat and add the chopped onion.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the ketchup, berbere spice, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Add the soaked lentils, red wine, and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir the azifa occasionally to prevent sticking.",
    "Serve the azifa hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
